{"tid":905033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[教練好撚慘] 一齊睇睇毒果事後點報呂麗瑤單案","createTime":"2018-11-16T22:11:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T04:36:28.000Z","uid":161430,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"25d06128183a513f0dae6d91cc077ef51e8851f4","tid":905033,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T22:11:57.000Z","msg":"今日新鮮出爐既新聞，首先黃教練冇罪，當然唔會有A1，<br />\n另外關於黃教練點樣面對外界目光嘅報導，當然係完全冇，<br />\n不過，反而就加插一遍報導，<br />\n標題係<strong>荷李活性醜聞 引發全球受害女性站出來</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181117/20548146\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F20548146&d=8z4ar%2F7dxXsMaV4BHpo%2B7wdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=1a570f17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F20548146&h=43726c44\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181117/20548146</a><br />\n<br />\n另外底下又有一篇報導，標題係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>港體壇中人敢撐不敢言</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181117/20548149\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F20548149&d=8z4ar%2F7dxXsMaV4BHpo%2B7wdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=a1daa3f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F20548149&h=1b117c12\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181117/20548149</a><br />\n<br />\n「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">雖然有關案件昨日的判決未必盡如人意</span></strong>，但可以想像事主在這一年承受着無比沉重的壓力及外界目光，一定不好受，經過她今次勇敢發聲，令香港社會各界對體壇性騷擾問題有更進一步的了解，相信有助減低同類事件再發生的可能。」<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母呢篇仲離譜，咁多野可以去報，但就特登要報呢啲，乜撚嘢「判決未必盡如人意」？公正嘅判決就係公正，就係講理性同證據，如果一個判決要去盡人意，即係人治而且代表你一早有前設<br />\n<br />\n仲有後面幾句又係偏袒到痴撚線，可以想像事主在這一年承受着無比沉重的壓力及外界目光，一定不好受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ? 要講慘，咁黃教練呢一年又承受咗啲咩呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁多資料可以報，你就整個「體壇中人敢撐不敢言」幾隻字做標題，再配合咁嘅內容，角度全部講女事主慘，黃教練脫罪係未盡如人意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n痴撚線人地無辜都比你班左膠妓者寫到奸計得逞咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黃教練有冇罪，左膠傳媒都已經判佢死罪"},{"pid":"e2659bac7fbc6b64f87083ad520d09851de9bfad","tid":905033,"uid":35814,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T23:53:02.000Z","msg":"為左賣多份報紙班友可以去到幾盡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a02f006028f1648cb0a0a09b16556360626a34","tid":905033,"uid":105567,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T00:06:07.000Z","msg":"毒果"},{"pid":"ea8bf7720e20b456ea8924f6c597f6a60e984e2a","tid":905033,"uid":66943,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T00:50:32.000Z","msg":"是旦 最緊要屌共"},{"pid":"60b30b78022996d0e84f38e37c80e82901c84d59","tid":905033,"uid":19527,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ea8bf7720e20b456ea8924f6c597f6a60e984e2a","tid":905033,"uid":66943,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T00:50:32.000Z","msg":"是旦 最緊要屌共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T00:54:59.000Z","msg":"屌共已經唔係佢地priority<br />\n而家最緊要係食玩同metoo"},{"pid":"ccd3e8444ac085cf519623109f4a801ed8bdc94c","tid":905033,"uid":13149,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"ea8bf7720e20b456ea8924f6c597f6a60e984e2a","tid":905033,"uid":66943,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T00:50:32.000Z","msg":"是旦 最緊要屌共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T00:57:55.000Z","msg":"毒果不嬲帶頭用蝗語字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4412ac2c850def23543d6dad6faab6bca652f4","tid":905033,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T01:23:39.000Z","